Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice flight off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That damn leopard jerk!\NNow I'm really pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay him back two times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:38.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:42.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:46.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:49.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:04.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:12.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:18.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:26.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:37.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:44.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:48.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:55.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:59.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:11.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:30.10,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Spandam's Scheme!\NThe Day the Sea Train Shook"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this filthy warehouse used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom's Workers shipbuilding\Ncompany's main office, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shipbuilding company?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom, Iceberg, and Cutty Flam...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a place that holds memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the three of you devoting\Nyourselves to building ships, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you call it a secret base...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of this place already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until we get what we want,\Nshipwright Cutty Flam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blueprints are not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... That's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Kalifa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell us right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is from eight years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you committed a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like Tom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a load of crap! Tom-san wasn't a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you know everything! You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a criminal. You should\Nknow what will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky... Don't interfere\Nin what I'm about to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything about Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything about Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}"Water Seven, 8 years ago"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Judicial Ship is coming in three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're finally having Tom's trial, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what'll happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did fulfill his promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry the received lumber into the dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the negotiation in St. Poplar go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. They're taking advantage\Nof us since we don't have materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same deal with the iron in San Faldo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shipyards will end up going into\Nthe red if things are that expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll work it out next time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is happy about\Nbeing able to cross the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I heard that trading with\Nother islands isn't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the town won't\Nchange even with the sea train...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But people are lively! The results\Nwon't show immediately, Iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once a man's done everything he could,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he should just resolutely keep his head high!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there. Are you Mr. Tom,\Na shipbuilding engineer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um...\N--Don't interrupt! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--I'd like to have a little conversation with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from Cipher Pol No. 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Spand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spandam-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,\Nbut my cannon salute hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is super! The Battle\NFranky No. 35 has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed a Sea King!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this size! It's a monster\Nthat must be at least 100m in length!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot... He never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, you bastard! Stop it, Stupid-berg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you keep building\Nstupid battleships one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, I'll destroy all\Nof them today for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!\NThey're my precious battleships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you mess with my ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...! Listen, Franky!\NYou killed a Sea King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that this is quite a lethal weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand your nerve,\Njust leaving dozens of them out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm gonna attack people with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with your intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling you to account for\Ncreating lethal weapons, Moron-ky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E... Excuse m...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san! Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron-ky is a disgrace to our company!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "Moron-ky" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me... Please hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I want you to apologize to me!\NAnd then, I want you to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the Government,\Naren't you? Is it about the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to talk alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with a man from the\NGovernment in the brick warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's name is Span... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Spanda-something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That official isn't from the Judicial Ship.\NWhat disorganized people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about it! I don't have\Nany blueprints for something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:10:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you're playing innocent\Njust because I've been acting humble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already investigated by going\Nback into the history of Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we check your belongings, the actual\Narticle will show up in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have the\Nauthority to investigate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure do, Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not,\Nour investigation already found out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you're a heinous criminal\Nwho built Gold Roger's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a criminal, we can\Ndo whatever we want with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government already knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you working here as a\Nshipwright instead of being in jail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are an intelligence agent,\Ncheck into it yourself. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! I'm not done talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom did fulfill his promise\Nwith the Judicial Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His charge will probably be written off\Nin the trial that will be held in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom is a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a serious charge related\Nto Roger will be written off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So something like that really does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, there are pirates who're\Nsniffing around for these blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, by chance, someone other than the\NGovernment got their hands on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there would no longer be any\Nmeans for us to fight against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more than ten years since the\Ndawn of the so-called Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates have been gaining power quickly\Nand keep increasing in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for carefree talk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about things like preventing the\Nrestoration of the ancient weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely because we uphold justice,\Nwe should have fangs like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll own the ancient weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and repel this Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Times are changing.\NThere's some truth to what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then obtain these blueprints\Nyou're talking about first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss it further afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave this matter to you, Spandam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Leave it to me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all my investigating,\NI finally got this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just gonna watch it go up in smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! If he's not a criminal,\Nit'll be a problem for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spandam-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with writing off the charge...\NHow cocky... Just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Call in five more intelligence agents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spandam-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg. Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--Both of you, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna entrust something\Nimportant to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why does something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Can humans make something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the worst monster ever\Nin the history of shipbuilding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government has become aware\Nof the existence of these blueprints
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has started taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be dangerous to keep them with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared... but I understand. We'll keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing! Hey, Iceberg,\Nlet's try building it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think a little before you say things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep them! If something like\Nthis is brought into this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the world will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you can do\Nwhatever you want with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even ditch them if it gets dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll tell you one more thing\Nthat I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, wait, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least put some pants on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Didn't you learn a lesson the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to town with only a swimsuit on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be another perv uproar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I'm just going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... To think that she's\Ntaking the trouble to prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,celebration dishes just because\NTom-san is being declared not guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't guilty from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tom-san! Iceberg! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the trial day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go get judged!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom's sentence is going to be be handed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This trial seems to be of\Nhigh interest to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of court spectators are getting on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the sea train, judge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I took a ride once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed incredible. I'm impressed\Nthat he really made it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the four islands are connected,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine no one would oppose his acquittal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tom here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for it to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! The spectators' gallery is gonna fill up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I have to see the moment he is\Ndeclared not guilty with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories.\NIt's already been 14 years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're these explosions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! A pirate raid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Where are they firing from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that fleet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen battleships like them!\NWhich pirate group is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with those\Nheavily armed ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N--Run towards the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! My son is stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell... took... took my ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky's ships are attacking the Judicial Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It's not Franky. He's in town right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly wouldn't do something\Nlike that! I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why this is trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop them, Iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they pirates? Or someone\Nfrom the Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Evacuate!\N--Don't stop! Hurry inland!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! They won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Who are they?!\NWho's screwing around with my ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge! Please hurry up!\NThis ship won't hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does that fleet belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The raid on the Judicial Ship was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then move on to the next\Nstep in the scenario immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sacrifice for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's start the trial... Tom's Workers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Judicial Ship will sink soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's go back\Nto the scrap heap island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the fleet is withdrawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I recognize those ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san! The ships are coming back this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're close to the shore!\NI think we can catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure went and did\Nsomething crazy with those ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people are running this way\Nfrom the scrap heap island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! No one is on the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This side, too. No one is on any of the ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Franky's, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Iceberg! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...! My Battle Frankys are a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg! Tom-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Both of you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ice--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That intelligence agent\Nwho came the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used your battleships.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got hurt by my battleships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over... and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand your nerve,\Njust leaving dozens of them out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling you to account for\Ncreating lethal weapons, Moron-ky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san got... hurt by my ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our skills can bring lethal\Nweapons into this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if you don't intend to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons hurt people despite your intentions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can even hurt those\Nwho mean a lot to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were taken in by the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna make us the culprits\Nfor attacking the Judicial Ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because they want to question Tom-san\Nas a criminal to obtain the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this... can you still\Nsay that you're innocent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't somehow stop them\Nfrom taking Tom-san away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forgive you for the rest of my life, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:33.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:38.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:47.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:56.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:06.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:15.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Tom-san. Because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you raiders who defy the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense! We didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth! I have business\Nwith this damn fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do with Tom-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for Tom's Workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End of the Legendary Man!\NThe Day the Sea Train Cried"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
